          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Responsible Transfer of Firearms Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to make it a crime to sell or transfer a firearm to prohibited person, unless the transferor takes reasonable steps to determine that the recipient is not prohibited from firearm possession. (Current law makes it a crime to sell or transfer a firearm to a prohibited person if the transferor knows or has reasonable cause to believe the recipient is prohibited from firearm possession.)</p>]]></text>
        </item>
